{"tid":521141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普政府要求參院 撥款180億 興建邊境圍牆","createTime":"2018-01-06T08:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T08:36:02.000Z","uid":147314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"73a6d1071ad59b4de678175974c33949683cbfda","tid":521141,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1373681-20180106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1373681-20180106.htm&d=MMseuoaUNqK7lbNC2G9Gkv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b6de1bde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1373681-20180106.htm&h=c88f32c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1373681-20180106.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普政府要求參院撥款180億興建邊境圍牆<br />\n2018-01-06<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1373681_1_L_20180106093611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1373681_1_L_20180106093611.jpg&h=d63e9d27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普政府要求180億美元，作為首階段興建邊境圍牆支出。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普政府向參議院要求180億美元撥款，在墨西哥邊境興建圍牆。<br />\n<br />\n美國海關和邊境保護局向參議院提交文件指，首階段工程包括未來十年新建508公里以及維修654公里圍牆。如果加上技術等其他支出，金額高達330億美元。<br />\n<br />\n預計工程在2027年完工時，美墨邊境將有長達3200公里的圍牆。<br />\n<br />\n建議被民主黨議員猛烈批評，指國會尋求在本月20日限期前，<span style=\"color: red;\">就來年度支出法案達成協議，避免聯邦政府停止運作之際，特朗普的撥款要求，足以令聯邦政府關閉。</span><br />\n<br />\n特朗普日前威脅，將興建圍牆，與解決「兒童暫緩遞解」問題的移民法案掛勾。興建圍牆是特朗普競選時其中一個主要政綱。"},{"pid":"4a11873b9fa8755d9ab610bf823c16d5b11ac8e6","tid":521141,"uid":73915,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"找數真漢子"},{"pid":"f364d0f0c6374a852ce44b9aeffff0e63f627f19","tid":521141,"uid":147314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T08:26:38.000Z","msg":"說好了的墨西哥付款呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":